Name: Zoo
Description: Each player must place 1 animal from their farm on the zoo

Name: Barn
Description: Can store up to two animals facedown (may add two immediately)

Name: Market Day
Description: Fill market til 2 animals per player. Twice around each player may purchase 1 animal or pass.

Name: Swap Meet
Description: Each player may take 1 animal from the player on their left

Name: Favor
Description: Look at top 5 cards of deck, put 1 in your hand and discard the rest
